<div class="content-page">
  <p class="page-intro">Clean Arcade is built on a simple idea: games should be fun, not frustrating. No ads, no sign-ups, no dark patterns.</p>

  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Zero Ads</h3>
      <p>No banner ads, no interstitials, no video ads before you play. The game loads and you play.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>No Tracking</h3>
      <p>No analytics, no cookies, no fingerprinting. We don't know who you are and we don't want to.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Local Saves</h3>
      <p>Your progress, high scores, and favorites are saved locally in your browser. They never leave your device.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>200 Games</h3>
      <p>Puzzle, arcade, card, board, word, strategy, sports, racing, and more. All playable in your browser.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Dark Mode</h3>
      <p>Respects your system preference or toggle manually. Easy on the eyes for late-night sessions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Mobile Friendly</h3>
      <p>Most games work on phones and tablets. Games that need a keyboard are clearly marked.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Fast Search</h3>
      <p>Find any game instantly with search. Filter by category, letter, or type a name.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Translated</h3>
      <p>Available in 30+ languages so everyone can play, wherever they are.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
